#  So as not to be disturbed by Ctrl-S ctrl-Q in terminals:
#  The default (legacy) behaviour of Ctrl-S is to stop
#+ terminal output; Ctrl-Q continues output.
#  I use Ctrl-S to navigate left in tmux and vim.
